*Tražio* je odgovor na pitanje. (He was looking for an answer to the question.)

On je *tražio* da se sastanemo. (He was looking for us to meet.)

Ona je *tražila* pomoć. (She was asking for help.)

*Tražili* su da se pridržava nekih pravila. (They were asking to follow certain rules.)

*Tražen* je odgovor. (An answer was being sought.)